\sqrt{x+\Delta x} = \sqrt{x} + \frac{1}{2\sqrt{x}}\Delta x
\approx
\sqrt{x+\Delta x} \approx \sqrt{x} + \frac{1}{2\sqrt{x}}\Delta x
\begin{align} \sqrt{x+\Delta x} - \sqrt{x} &=(\sqrt{x+\Delta x} - \sqrt{x})\frac{\sqrt{x+\Delta x} + \sqrt{x}}{\sqrt{x+\Delta x} + \sqrt{x}}\\ &=\frac{(\sqrt{x+\Delta x} - \sqrt{x})(\sqrt{x+\Delta x} + \sqrt{x})}{\sqrt{x+\Delta x} + \sqrt{x}}\\ &=\frac{(x+\Delta x) - x}{\sqrt{x+\Delta x} + \sqrt{x}}\\ &=\frac{\Delta x}{\sqrt{x+\Delta x} + \sqrt{x}}\\ &\approx\frac{\Delta x}{2\sqrt{x}}\\ \end{align} 
\sqrt{x+\Delta x} \approx \sqrt{x} 
\Delta x \to 0
